BMI and calorie calculator

Create an application that calculates the user's BMI and estimated daily caloric needs.
The program should allow the user to enter the following data: height (cm), weight (kg), age, gender, and physical activity level.
The program should calculate:
• BMI (Body Mass Index) and display the category (underweight, normal, overweight, obese).
• Caloric requirement (BMR) using the Mifflin-St. Jeor formula.
